N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 436.11 - Claiming

State Regulations

Claims for reimbursement for payments of kinship
guardianship assistance and non-recurring guardianship expenses must be made by
each social services district in such form and manner and at such times and for
such periods as required by the office. Notes
